00:35:34.060 --> 00:35:37.190
so I definitely wouldn't
encourage anyone to, you know,

00:35:37.190 --> 00:35:40.120
eat 20 pounds of it
a day or anything

00:35:40.120 --> 00:35:42.710
like that, as tempting as it is.

00:35:42.710 --> 00:35:44.730
I struggle not eating
so much of it.

00:35:44.730 --> 00:35:48.360
But, you know, in moderation
it is much better for you

00:35:48.360 --> 00:35:53.860
than a artificially
chemical laden product.

00:35:53.860 --> 00:35:56.300
And the natural cacao
butter too,

00:35:56.300 --> 00:35:58.270
because there's higher
