00:36:01.540 --> 00:36:06.930
That fat is pretty high in
omega 6s and it's not --

00:36:06.930 --> 00:36:09.670
you know, it's much better for
you than like artificial waxes

00:36:09.670 --> 00:36:11.800
and fats that they put
in Hershey's to get

00:36:11.800 --> 00:36:13.420
that same chocolate texture.

