00:36:16.590 --> 00:36:18.120
You have to put something
in to make it feel

00:36:18.120 --> 00:36:19.600
like chocolate in your mouth.

00:36:19.600 --> 00:36:22.260
And all that stuff is
artificially produced

00:36:22.260 --> 00:36:24.310
and it's not great.

00:36:24.310 --> 00:36:25.640
&gt;&gt; Samuel Carvalho: Yeah,

