00:53:21.230 --> 00:53:24.260
They're called the Fine Cocoa
and Chocolate Institute.

00:53:24.260 --> 00:53:29.650
And they are setting up
a standard of basically

00:53:29.650 --> 00:53:33.200
like assessment for
preventing those things.

00:53:33.200 --> 00:53:35.210
And we follow that standard.

00:53:35.210 --> 00:53:37.160
So we visit our farms.

00:53:37.160 --> 00:53:38.780
We talk to our people.

00:53:38.780 --> 00:53:43.610
And we go down and we make
sure that what we pay directly

00:53:43.610 --> 00:53:45.450
to the farm is actually
getting passed

00:53:45.450 --> 00:53:47.680
down in wages to the workers.

00:53:47.680 --> 00:53:49.880
We tour the farms
and we make sure

00:53:49.880 --> 00:53:54.130
that those agroforestry
principles are actually being

00:53:54.130 --> 00:53:57.210
followed and that they're
meeting all of those standards.

00:53:57.210 --> 00:54:01.860
And we also talk to other
industry professionals

00:54:01.860 --> 00:54:03.390
who are monitoring those things.

00:54:03.390 --> 00:54:06.190
And that's what's
interesting right now

00:54:06.190 --> 00:54:09.250
about the chocolate industry,
is all of that is growing.

00:54:09.250 --> 00:54:12.790
It's very much at its
infancy, those changes

00:54:12.790 --> 00:54:15.190
and people putting together
groups and organizations

00:54:15.190 --> 00:54:17.320
to help enforce those changes.

00:54:17.320 --> 00:54:19.650
So it's all very new.

00:54:19.650 --> 00:54:23.160
And basically how we do
it is we've set standards

00:54:23.160 --> 00:54:26.700
for ourselves and we've set
standards for who we will work

00:54:26.700 --> 00:54:29.220
with and who we won't
work with, and we just try

00:54:29.220 --> 00:54:32.720
to follow those guidelines
as best we can,

00:54:32.720 --> 00:54:34.910
and try to be adaptable
and partner

00:54:34.910 --> 00:54:36.280
with those other companies

00:54:36.280 --> 00:54:39.230
that are setting those
rules and standards.

00:54:39.230 --> 00:54:40.680
Yeah, thank you.

00:54:40.680 --> 00:54:41.980
That's a great question.

00:54:41.980 --> 00:54:44.770
&gt;&gt; We have time for
